Help Type: topic
Topic: command

Command Overview

Object commands:
  wikigraph <wikigraph-uri-with-sdpub-locator> search <query>
  wikigraph <wikigraph-uri-with-sdpub-locator> list
  wikigraph <object-uri> get
  wikigraph <object-uri> related
  wikigraph <object-uri> evidence
  wikigraph next <cursor>
  wikigraph <object-uri> pack

URI routing:
  `search`, `list`, `get`, `related`, `evidence`, and `pack` use Wiki Graph URIs, not bare filesystem paths.
  Read `wikigraph help uri` before using object commands; skipping the URI rules commonly leads to invalid commands.

Archive commands:
  wikigraph create <archive.sdpub>
  wikigraph export <archive.sdpub>
  wikigraph estimate <archive.sdpub>
  wikigraph index <archive.sdpub>
  wikigraph transform [options]

Generation:
  wikigraph queue add <archive.sdpub> --chapter <id> --task <reading-graph|reading-summary|knowledge-graph> --accept-cost

Maintenance:
  wikigraph meta <archive.sdpub>
  wikigraph cover <archive.sdpub>
  wikigraph chapter <action> <archive.sdpub>
  wikigraph config status
